name: Condor 767-330ER [D-ABUD] Takeoff from Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Yay, Condor! :D I'm glad they're back again for this summer. I just love seeing their 767s with those gigantic winglets! Anyway, here is D-ABUD taking off from Calgary's new runway. Same spot as my previous videos, but you can still get a pretty nice view of 17L takeoffs! Hope you enjoy, and stay tuned for another video from the temporary spot that I went to for the first operations tomorrow!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
